-------------
HOW TO DEPLOY
-------------

1.- Install wtdeploy:

    1.1.- workon your_virtual_env
    1.2.- pip install fabric
    1.3.- pip install -U -e git+git://github.com/ahmontero/wtdeploy.git#egg=wtdeploy

2.- Set your svn username and password in 'development' method at 'fabfile.py':
    env.repo_user = 'your_username'
    env.repo_password = 'your_password'

3.- cd project_root

4.- fab development push
